&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with Product, Sales, Engineering and leadership to support the pre-sale design process for highly customized enterprise opportunities. This includes helping customers understand how EvolutionIQ’s solutions will integrate with their claims systems, policies, eligibility feeds, data flows, and workflows, and shaping the transformation narrative that allows executive sponsors to secure buy-in internally. You will also help customers distinguish between configurable product capabilities, integration needs, and areas that may require deeper product or implementation planning.&lt;/p&gt;
