&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code Quality &amp;amp; Best Practices:&lt;/strong&gt; Set the standard for software engineering practices within data—including version control (Git), CI/CD, data testing, observability, and comprehensive documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
